author: Daily Press staff
title: Team Bishop prevails in Cup, opens 10-7 lead
text:
Courtesy photo Paragould Cup champs 
Team Bishop defeated Team Davenport in the 17th annual Paragould Cup last weekend at Paragould Country Club. Members of Team Bishop include (from left): front — Sam Dickey, Mark Miller, Steve Latting, Sherell Johnson, David Acuff, Randy Bishop (captain), Johnny Stanford and John Hopkins; back — Jim Calhoon, Kendall Jetton, Bud Wallace, Kevin Ward, Van Winton, Mike Cline, and Nate Burnett. Posted: Monday, October 5, 2015 11:45 pm 
Team Bishop upped its lead in the Paragould Cup competition with a 22-18 win over Team Davenport this past weekend at Paragould Country Club.
